# source - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9mELEARcxJo&list=PL9ooVrP1hQOGyFc60sExNX1qBWJyV5IMb

Hadoop - batch processing
Spark - real time processing

Installion steps- 
1. Install JDK 
2. Download apache spark2.0 and extract
tar -xvf spark2.0.gzip
3. App to path (SPARK_HOME , PATH)
export SPARK_HOME=/home/Desktop/spark
export PATH=$PATH:$SPARK_HOME/bin
4. Verify spark working
spark-shell  #This will open scala shell. Scala is officially part of spark form 2.0 version






